&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/exploring-the-benefits-of-ai-bots-for-forex-trading-in-forex-markets/"&gt;Exploring the Benefits of AI Bots for Forex Trading in Forex Markets&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com"&gt;AI News&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=113483</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 12:38:44 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Building self-improving tax agents with Codex</title><link>https://openai.com/index/building-self-improving-tax-agents-with-codex</link><description>See how OpenAI, Thrive, and Crete built a self-improving tax agent with Codex, automating filings, improving accuracy, and accelerating workflows.</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://openai.com/index/building-self-improving-tax-agents-with-codex</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 07:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Reachy Mini goes fully local</title><link>https://huggingface.co/blog/local-reachy-mini-conversation</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://huggingface.co/blog/local-reachy-mini-conversation</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Shipping a Trillion Parameters With a Hub Bucket: Delta Weight Sync in TRL</title><link>https://huggingface.co/blog/delta-weight-sync</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://huggingface.co/blog/delta-weight-sync</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>